  "text": "In this section, we show applications of our general technique. We start with the problem discussed in the introduction: Energy Efficient Routing. Recall, that Andrews et al. [CITATION_1] gave an O (k + log q−1 Δ)-approximation algorithm for this problem where k = |D| and Δ = max i ∈D d i (Theorem 8 in Andrews et al. [CITATION_2] ). We give an (1 + ε)A q -approximation algorithm for any fixed ε > 0. ",
